headline: Tyler Technologies (NYSE:TYL) Expands Partnership With Kenosha To Modernize City Operations
summary: Tyler Technologies (NYSE:TYL) recently signed an agreement with the city of Kenosha, Wisconsin, to upgrade its ERP system with Tyler’s integrated software solutions. This agreement, combined with the integration of Equifax’s The Work Number, positions the company to enhance its product offering in the public sector. headline: City of Kenosha, Wisconsin, Selects Public Administration Solutions from Tyler Technologies
summary: PLANO, Texas, June 03, 2025--Tyler Technologies announced it has signed an agreement with the city of Kenosha, Wisconsin, for multiple Tyler solutions.
